Henry Friedlander v. Claire Friedlander Claire Deutsch Friedlander v. Henry Z. Friedlander (6946) (7425)

Spallone, Daly and O’Connell, Js.

Argued October 12 decision released October 18, 1989 Henry Z. Friedlander, pro se, the appellant (plaintiff in the first case, defendant in the second case). Saul Kwartin, for the appellee (defendant in the first case, plaintiff in the second case). Per Curiam.

There is no error in either case.
